    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4301580/extras/711f3a31ea231de705f580a1ab46135e.avif?t=1769610381\" width=1241 height=457 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为了更多，你能走多远？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和你的 <strong>朋友</strong> 组队，化身 <strong>搞怪浣熊</strong>，<strong>潜入</strong> <strong>程序生成</strong> 的 <strong>远古遗迹</strong>，为负责挖掘的鼹鼠们 <strong>带出魔法遗物</strong>——在遗迹（以及你们的队伍）分崩离析之前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4301580/extras/41a350516340200000af5a276f5a2365.poster.avif?t=1769610381\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4301580/extras/41a350516340200000af5a276f5a2365.webm?t=1769610381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4301580/extras/41a350516340200000af5a276f5a2365.mp4?t=1769610381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >团队 vs 自私</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宝藏是力量……也是麻烦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遗物奖励由所有人共享</strong>。但你拿的 <strong>每一件额外物品</strong> 都会加速你的 <strong>个人进度</strong>，同时让你更 <strong>缓慢</strong>、更 <strong>吵闹</strong>。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >粉碎战利品，购买升级</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把 <strong>战利品变成金币</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用它们购买 <strong>道具</strong> 和 <strong>升级</strong>，在 <strong>鼹鼠轮盘</strong> 上豪赌一把，或者——运气好——逛逛 <strong>Mammon</strong> 的 <strong>交易</strong>。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >知道何时撤离</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遗物只是半程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还得 <strong>在压力下逃出生天</strong>，然后 <strong>一起做决定</strong>：<strong>现在结算，还是孤注一掷</strong> 去下一层换更大的回报。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mammon 的诅咒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遗迹并非无人看守。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mammon</strong>、<strong>贪婪恶魔</strong>，以及他的仆从正在注视。若队伍偷得太多，他会 <strong>诅咒整支队伍</strong>，最贪的那只浣熊甚至可能反过来威胁自己的朋友。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >程序遗迹，无尽轮回</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一层都会重洗</strong>：布局、陷阱、怪物与谜题不断变化，计划很快就会崩盘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿出全部本事：<strong>探索、配合、技巧、潜行与快速决策</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4301580/extras/4f607f8742bc41139fc586821c2e73ea.poster.avif?t=1769610381\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4301580/extras/4f607f8742bc41139fc586821c2e73ea.webm?t=1769610381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4301580/extras/4f607f8742bc41139fc586821c2e73ea.mp4?t=1769610381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
